properties.Overview:
The Breached Motherboard is an [https://minershaven.fandom.com/wiki/Evolved_Reborn Evolved Reborn]-[https://minershaven.fandom.com/wiki/Item_Tiers tier] [https://minershaven.fandom.com/wiki/Furnaces furnace] added in the [https://minershaven.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Reincarnation_Update Reincarnation Update].

The Breached Motherboard works similarly to its predecessor, [https://minershaven.fandom.com/wiki/Invasive_Cyberlord Invasive Cyberlord], in that it has 3 upgrade beams above the furnace, each multiplying ore value by x2 for a total multiplier of x8. With an initial x500 multiplier, if all beams are hit, this furnace will process ores at a multiplier of x4000.

{{Collapse|title=Appearance}}
It looks like the [https://minershaven.fandom.com/wiki/Invasive_Cyberlord Invasive Cyberlord] but bigger, has more monitors and servers and seems to have a circuitry effect branching out. There is also an antenna on either side.
{{/Collapse}}

